 extended into the pharmaceutical industry with solutions that help in the manufacture of medicine we create a wide range of innovative and sustainable products for the industrial markets search products read about previous market energy and water  view all markets view all markets read about next markets infrastructure  agriculture  dow the human element at work find global websites and locations region africa asia pacific europe latin america middle east north america country our roots run deep dow innovations help farmers feed the growing world play video what can we help you find home markets and solutions agriculture dow businesses in agriculture see how dow is making a difference on farms around the world dow agrosciences dow agriculture stories and videos dow is helping to fight food insecurity in africa isoclast™ is fighting plant pests in  countries chemicals are found everywhere – even in organic produce crop defense solutions let farmers to do more with fewer chemicals dow helps protect historic midway islands from invasive plants pdf the recipe for a healthier world begins with a healthier oil dow in agriculture since the s dow’s agricultural business has been discovering developing and bringing sustainable solutions to market for the growing world we are committed to helping farmers increase their crop productivity through higher yields better varieties and targeted weed insect and disease control our products and services balance the needs of boosting agricultural productivity while preserving the environment we create a wide range of innovative and sustainable products for agriculture markets search products read about previous market product safety  view all markets view all markets read about next markets automotive  dow chemical company  wikipedia dow chemical company from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from dow chemicals jump to navigation search the dow chemical co type public traded as nyse dow sp  component industry chemicals founded  founder herbert henry dow headquarters midland michigan us area served worldwide key people andrew n liveris chairman president and ceo products chemicals plastics performance chemicals catalysts coatings crop technology crude oil and natural gas exploration and production revenue   billion fy   operating income   billion fy  profit   billion fy  total assets   billion fy  total equity   billion fy  subsidiaries dow agrosciences llc union carbide corp rohm and haas angus chemical company dow roofing systems website wwwdowcom the dow chemical company commonly referred to as dow is an american multinational chemical corporation headquartered in midland michigan united states as of  it is the secondlargest chemical manufacturer in the world by revenue after basf and as of february  the thirdlargest chemical company in the world by market capitalization after basf and dupont it ranked second in the world by chemical production in  dow manufactures plastics chemicals and agricultural products with a presence in about  countries it employs about  people worldwide the company has seven different major operating segments with a wide variety of products made by each one dows  sales totaled approximately  billion dow has been called the chemical companies chemical company in that most of its sales are to other industries rather than endusers dow sells directly to endusers primarily in the human and animal health and consumer products markets dow is a member of the american chemistry council the company tagline is solutionism contents  products  performance plastics  performance chemicals  water purification  agricultural sciences  basic plastics  basic chemicals  hydrocarbons and energy  history  early history  diversification and expansion  nuclear weapons  vietnam war napalm and agent orange  dow corning breast implants  bhopal disaster  dbcp  tax evasion  recent mergers acquisitions and reorganization  s – transition from geographic alignment to global business units 